_sText:
This is my Cod4 map in Counter strike source. It's suppose to be the Shipment map, you know the smallest map in Cod4. In this version (2) i have fixed the spawns and made ladders so you can reach the highest metal crate, but you can also jump between the crates by jumping up on the wall. Anyway, enjoy!

If you got any advice on improvement, send me them and I can rebuild my map.
